  m_Name: Dlg_Tutorial_GM_AfterShovel
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - Now the most exciting of the four. Fire.
  - You have a fine furnace in your lab, but it sits cold and unlit.
  - Gather some wood to feed it. Three branches should be plenty.
